# ==============================================================================
# .Renviron -- R Environment Configuration (project-level)
# ==============================================================================
#
# Copy this file to .Renviron in the project root (it is gitignored).
# Restart your R session after changes (Session > Restart R in RStudio).
#
# This file is read by R on startup BEFORE any scripts run.
# Values set here override auto-detection in R/00_config.R.
#
# IMPORTANT: Create .Renviron in THIS directory (project root), NOT in ~/
# A user-level ~/.Renviron would affect ALL R projects on your machine.
# ==============================================================================

# Force local testing mode (overrides OS auto-detection in R/00_config.R)
# Default behavior: Windows = local testing, Linux = HiPerGator production
# Uncomment the line below to force local mode on any OS (e.g., Linux VM):
# R_TESTING_ENV=local
